<D>__{no!}
<A>__{cutting off further conversation, he looks out at: the mountains of greece with longing. billy stares back at: the driver whose eyes now move away from the rear view mirror under the pressure of the stare. sound off loud machinery. billy turning in rear window, we see a turkish halftrack pulling alongside the cab, soldiers waving their arms for the cabdriver to get out of the way. another angle the halftrack pulls level. the cabdriver slows down, with a curse. billy beads of sweat trickle his brow the personnel carrier, disinterested, pulls past. billy breathes heavily with nervous relief.}
